com.percussion.pso.workflow
Class PublishEditionService

java.lang.Object
  com.percussion.pso.workflow.PublishEditionService
All Implemented Interfaces:
InitializingBean
public class PublishEditionService
extends Object
implements InitializingBean

The PublishEdition service starts an edition. This class used to start the remote publisher via HTTP, but in 6.6 we use the IPSRxPublisherService. The baseUrl, cmsUser, cmsPassword, listenerPort and retryCount parameters are no longer used. The getters and setters remain in place for backwards compatibility.

Author:
DavidBenua
